name: golang-projects
tagline: A common github repo for go-lang projects
body:
### Welcome to golang-projects.
This is a unified repository for all golang based projects. The two primary projects are [go-dfs](https://github.com/sjoshi6/go-lang-Projects/tree/master/go-dfs) - A distributed file system using redis and [go-lbapp](https://github.com/sjoshi6/go-lang-Projects/tree/master/go-lbapp) - A backend JSON based API for the location based social networking app.

Currently, the work is in progress for the [go-lbapp](https://github.com/sjoshi6/go-lang-Projects/tree/master/go-lbapp) project
